cButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5443144\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_5443144\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 06, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hqx1699858286844.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hqx1699858286844.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hqx1699858286844.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hqx1699858286844\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Generate a random string, raw data of a specified length, or a number between 0 and\n\t\t1.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__section_w12997ab1b5b1_w12998ab1b5_w12999ab1\"><p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">$random(\"number\")</code></p><code class=\"ph codeph\">$random(\"string | raw \",\n\t\t\t\tLength)</code></section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__section_jkb_4nv_kzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d246824e60\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__table_sd3_qnv_kzb\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__table_sd3_qnv_kzb__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__table_sd3_qnv_kzb__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__table_sd3_qnv_kzb__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_sd3_qnv_kzb__entry__1\">Topic</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_sd3_qnv_kzb__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_sd3_qnv_kzb__entry__3\">Data type of return values.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_sd3_qnv_kzb__entry__1\">Length</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_sd3_qnv_kzb__entry__2\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_sd3_qnv_kzb__entry__3\">Data length of return values which ranges from 1 to 128.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__section_zj1_14v_kzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d246824e126\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">$random</code> returns three types of values. The type depends on the\n\t\t\t\tTopic.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__table_nwq_m4v_kzb\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Random values that can be returned by $random</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__table_nwq_m4v_kzb__entry__1\">Topic</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__table_nwq_m4v_kzb__entry__2\">Returned value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_nwq_m4v_kzb__entry__1\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_nwq_m4v_kzb__entry__2\">Printable string with a specified length.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_nwq_m4v_kzb__entry__1\">Raw</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_nwq_m4v_kzb__entry__2\">Raw data with a specified length.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_nwq_m4v_kzb__entry__1\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_nwq_m4v_kzb__entry__2\">Number between 0 and 1.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\">If an error occurs, a negative value identifying the specific error is stored in\n\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">$procerror</code>, and an empty string (\"\") is returned.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <code class=\"ph codeph\">$procerror</code> following\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">$random</code></span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__2\">Error constant</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__3\">Meaning in context of $random</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__1\">-1110</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">UPROCERR_TOPIC</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__3\">Topic name not known.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__1\">-1001</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">UPROCERR_STRING </code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__3\">Generate random string failed.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__1\">-1002</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">UPROCERR_NUMERIC</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__3\">Generate random number failed.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__1\">-1007</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">UPROCERR_RAW</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__3\">Generate random raw data failed.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__1\">-1203</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">UPROCERR_RANGE</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"hqx1699858286844__table_mk2_vpv_kzb__entry__3\">Value out of range. <code class=\"ph codeph\">Length</code> provided is not within the range 1 to\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t128.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__section_qfl_kqv_kzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d246824e304\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__section_ffm_lqv_kzb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d246824e313\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The function <code class=\"ph codeph\">$random</code> generates a random string, raw data of a specified\n\t\t\t\tlength, ranging from 1 to 128, or a random numeric value between 0 and 1. When\n\t\t\t\tgenerating a numeric value, the length argument is not used. If the topic is string\n\t\t\t\tor raw data, the length argument is required.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__section_n2q_hwg_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d246824e326\">Example: Using <code class=\"ph codeph\">$random</code></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows how to use <code class=\"ph codeph\">$random</code> to generate a numeric, string,\n\t\t\t\tor raw data result and calculates its length:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104hqx1699858286844_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"hqx1699858286844__codeblock_q5l_lrv_kzb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">variables \n    numeric len, randomNum, strLen, byteLen \n    string  resStr \n    raw resRaw \n\nendvariables \n\nlen = 15 \n\nrandomNum = $random(\"Number\")  ; randomNum = 0.73350636388324717805777460567361290307  \nstrLen = $length(RandomNum)    ; strLen= 40  \nresStr = $random(\"String\", len); resStr = \"usVf#G6\"jj{kN4a\"  \nstrLen = $length(resStr)       ; strLen= 15  \nresRaw = $random(\"Raw\", len)   ; resRaw = \"|i|3Np{]1Rz{O|Y+|${-|kr\"  \nbyteLen = $length(resRaw)      ; byteLen = 15, byte length, Setting $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES = 1 \nstrLen = $length(resRaw)       ; strLen= 23, character length, Setting $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES = 0 or not specified.\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rkb1689666715569.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$encode</a><p>Encrypt data, sign messages with digital signatures, or convert data from one encoding scheme to another.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/djt1699862643714.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$decode</a><p>Decrypt or decode data, or verify a message by means of a digital signature.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yeo1699862389212.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>numeric</a><p>Uniface data type specifying a number to a maximum of 38 decimal places, including +, -, and decimal point .</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/toc1665703008287.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$length</a><p>Return the length of the specified argument.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iej1741086838875.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES</a><p>Specify if function $length returns the length in bytes or characters for arguments with datatype Raw.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5443144\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5443144\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$random Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 06, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Generate a random string, raw data of a specified length, or a number between 0 and 1. $random(\"number\") $random(\"string | raw \", Length) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Topic String Data type of return values. Length Numeric Data length of return values which ranges from 1 to 128. Return Values $random returns three types of values. The type depends on the Topic. Table 2. Random values that can be returned by $random Topic Returned value String Printable string with a specified length. Raw Raw data with a specified length. Numeric Number between 0 and 1. If an error occurs, a negative value identifying the specific error is stored in $procerror , and an empty string (\"\") is returned. Table 3. Values commonly returned by $procerror following $random Value Error constant Meaning in context of $random -1110 UPROCERR_TOPIC Topic name not known. -1001 UPROCERR_STRING Generate random string failed. -1002 UPROCERR_NUMERIC Generate random number failed. -1007 UPROCERR_RAW Generate random raw data failed. -1203 UPROCERR_RANGE Value out of range. Length provided is not within the range 1 to 128. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The function $random generates a random string, raw data of a specified length, ranging from 1 to 128, or a random numeric value between 0 and 1. When generating a numeric value, the length argument is not used. If the topic is string or raw data, the length argument is required. Example: Using $random The following example shows how to use $random to generate a numeric, string, or raw data result and calculates its length: Explain this code variables numeric len, randomNum, strLen, byteLen string resStr raw resRaw endvariables len = 15 randomNum = $random(\"Number\") ; randomNum = 0.73350636388324717805777460567361290307 strLen = $length(RandomNum) ; strLen= 40 resStr = $random(\"String\", len); resStr = \"usVf#G6\"jj{kN4a\" strLen = $length(resStr) ; strLen= 15 resRaw = $random(\"Raw\", len) ; resRaw = \"|i|3Np{]1Rz{O|Y+|${-|kr\" byteLen = $length(resRaw) ; byteLen = 15, byte length, Setting $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES = 1 strLen = $length(resRaw) ; strLen= 23, character length, Setting $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES = 0 or not specified. Copy Related Links $encode Encrypt data, sign messages with digital signatures, or convert data from one encoding scheme to another. $decode Decrypt or decode data, or verify a message by means of a digital signature. numeric Uniface data type specifying a number to a maximum of 38 decimal places, including +, -, and decimal point . $length Return the length of the specified argument. $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES Specify if function $length returns the length in bytes or characters for arguments with datatype Raw. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}